ctually so hard that they give XP to many druids too.<BR>They also got mobs that requires a good group, but they can actually get groups on the other hand.<BR>When guilds are going to help on epic quests, then they tend to help the ones that are near the end. When looking at the necros in the guild, then they all miss half or more of the quest and fact it looks like they have just begun it.<BR>Usually druids gets their epic faster than the necros and the effect on the druid epic is better than the necro epics, so why even bother.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
