        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">We all know what needs to be done:<BR>1. PETS. Up the HP on 53/56/59 pets, make the 59 pet "worth" the 100k plus I am probably going to have to pay for it.</P><P>2. Spells, why do our spells drop rarely off high level MOBs deep inside tough dungeons where we arent wanted?. Why cant these spells be either quests or purchaseable.</P><P>3. DuckStick. Nuff said.</P><P>4. Spell upgrades. Night time spells?, what for?.  Why does our "Child" class get upgrades to spells that the "parent" class doesnt?. I dont know a lot about OOP but isnt it supposed to be the other way round?.</P><P>5. Essence emeralds, get rid of em. I dont even have this spell and have turned it down on several occasions. I know how hard it is to get XP in this game, why the hell am I going to cause someone else all that pain?.</P><P>6. Bone chips, this was probably originally in game as something that was a "payment" for how powerful we were. Well we arent now. Put em on vendors. Hell put em on ONE vendor somewhere accessable and make em expensive (25pp per stack or something) it will still be the busiest vendor in game.</P><P> Basically I aggree with everything you said Smaaug. But we all know that absolutely NOTHING is going to be done about it. The Wizzies are screaming and the safehouse is gloating. They arent going to listen to us.</P><P>I work in IT, watching VI is like an object lesson in how not to roll out software.</P><P>Bow Down for a Defiler walks amongst you!<BR>55 DE Necromancer<BR>Karana server<BR>Proud Member of The Silent Watch<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td bgcolor="dimgray" valign="top">
        
