        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">fix the fucking resist rates on all mobs across the board.</P><P>allow us to be able to buff our pets so that they have higher hps and greater resists across the board.  </P><P>The above changes would help casters in general and our brothers in arms - the magicians who now that I think about it, might have it worse than us.  I dont give a fuck about pet graphics or animations, our fucked up epic or our sol spells.  I believe what I ask is nothing too overbalancing and is something that should have been implemented when kunark came out.</P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
